QuestData.Title: The Dynamic Duo
QuestData.Description: Excellent job.$B$B<Shauly winks at you.>$B$BI think they're buying it. Now, when I send you up to speak with my associates at the Stormspire, there won't be any suspicion at all.$B$BYou'll want to look for Action Jaxon and Audi the Needle up there. They'll tell you everything you need to know. Tell 'em Shauly sent you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Audi the Needle at the Stormspire in Netherstorm.
QuestData.RewardText: <You introduce yourself and tell Audi that Shauly sent you.>$B$BAh, yes, we've been expecting someone to help us, err -- move some, uh, merchandise.
